# North East Essex – Type 2 Together groups
Listed below are the Type 2 Together groups that are currently up and running
in the North East Essex area. Please note that meeting dates are subject to
change so please contact the Eastern regional team if you'd like to join a
group - eastern@diabetes.org.uk (or to update your listing).
